        public LocalDateRange​(java.time.LocalDate start,

        Create a range with start and end. A negative duration will use start as end and computes the start of this range by subtracting length from end.
        Parameters:
        start - of the range
        length - length of the range

        end - of range

        public boolean isBefore​(java.time.LocalDate when)
